âœ… The Sentence You Must Add to Use Bootstrap
Place this inside the <head> section of your HTML file:


<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
***This line activates Bootstrap on your page â€” so now you can use any of its built-in classes (functions/styles).***

âœ… Some Useful Bootstrap "Functions" (Classes)
These are not functions like in JavaScript â€” they are CSS classes that do specific things when you apply them.

